title: WHAT THE HELL Is Going On in Taiwan?!
description:
Joe Biden announced a stunning new foreign policy stance regarding the defense of Taiwan against China ... and the White House is walking it back. We go into the details of Biden's brain fart and what it means. Also, people are catching monkeypox, so that's a thing now. And we're back to canceling Dave Chappelle. #taiwan #china #monkeypox #DaveChappelle
